(71, 'Discussion on Inviting Movie Star Maged ElMasri:\nThe team agreed to invite movie star Maged ElMasri as a special guest to attract more attention to the fundraising event.', '09:46:00', 65, '2023-07-12 13:52:30', '2023-07-12 13:52:30'),
(72, 'Selection of Event Venue:\nAfter considering several options and their respective pros and cons, [Stony HillInn] was selected as the most suitable venue for the event.', '09:55:00', 65, '2023-07-12 13:54:53', '2023-07-12 13:54:53'),
