(329, 'Purpose of the Meeting :\n\n- Clearly state the purpose of the meeting: discussing the process of holding a Ramadan celebration for orphaned children in the village of Al-Qubeiba.\n\n- Emphasize the importance of providing a memorable experience for the children during Ramadan.', '09:40:00', 113, '2023-11-28 11:25:20', '2023-11-28 11:25:20'),
(330, '- Presentation of Background Information\n\n-Provide an overview of the orphaned children in the village of Al-Qubeiba and their current living conditions.\n\n-Highlight the significance of holding a Ramadan celebration to bring joy and happiness to their lives.', '10:00:00', 113, '2023-11-28 11:26:18', '2023-11-28 11:26:18'),
(331, '- Discussion on Iftar Party Arrangements\n\nBrainstorm and discuss the logistics of organizing an iftar party for the orphaned children.\n\nDetermine the location, date, and time for the event.\n\nConsider food arrangements, including catering or volunteer preparation, dietary restrictions, and safety measures.', '10:30:00', 113, '2023-11-28 11:28:02', '2023-11-28 11:28:02'),
(332, '- Budget and Fundraising\n\n-Assess the financial requirements for organizing the Ramadan celebration.\n\n-Develop a budget plan to track expenses and ensure efficient resource allocation.', '11:00:00', 113, '2023-11-28 11:29:11', '2023-11-28 11:29:11'),
(333, '- Next Steps and Timeline\n\n- Summarize the key action points and decisions made during the meeting.\n\n- Share the agreed-upon timeline for completing tasks and achieving milestones.\n\n-Clarify any follow-up actions or additional meetings required.', '11:30:00', 113, '2023-11-28 11:30:01', '2023-11-28 11:30:01'),
