(336, '- Purpose of the Meeting\n\nDiscussion on transferring funds to support the Ramadan celebration for orphaned children in the village of Al-Qubeiba\nOverview of the planned Iftar party and entertainment programs', '10:00:00', 114, '2023-11-28 12:03:25', '2023-11-28 12:03:25'),
(337, '- Financial Report:\n\nMrs, Naiera Hamad presented the current financial status of New Egypt Group, highlighting available funds and the budget for the Ramadan celebration.', '10:25:00', 114, '2023-11-28 12:04:57', '2023-11-28 12:04:57'),
(338, '- Proposal for Fund Transfer:\n\nMrs, Naiera Hamed presented a proposal for transferring funds to support the Ramadan celebration, providing a breakdown of expenses for the Iftar party and entertainment programs.', '11:00:00', 114, '2023-11-28 12:15:09', '2023-11-28 12:15:09'),
(339, '- Closing:\n\nThe meeting was adjourned, and members were thanked for their active participation.', '11:30:00', 114, '2023-11-28 12:16:22', '2023-11-28 12:16:22'),
