(342, '- Presentation on Al-qubeiba Village :\n\nProvide background information about Al-qubeiba village, including its location, demographics, and socio-economic conditions.\n\nHighlight the specific need for clothing among the children in the village.', '10:00:00', 116, '2023-12-15 15:59:42', '2023-12-15 15:59:42'),
