(367, '-  Discussion and Approval of Bank Deposit from Haya Karima Donation Campaign :\n-The board discussed the decision to deposit USD 150,000 into the bank. It was noted that this amount represents proceeds from donations from the campaign to support Haya Karima.', '09:40:00', 121, '2024-03-18 14:45:03', '2024-03-18 14:45:18'),
