(370, '- Discussion on Breaking the $150,000 Deposit :\nThe board discussed the proposal to break the $150,000 deposit that was made in October 2021 from the proceeds of donations from the campaign to support the Haya Karima initiative.', '09:50:00', 122, '2024-03-18 15:33:29', '2024-03-18 15:33:29'),
(371, '- Bank Notification Regarding the Deposit:\n\nIt was informed from the bank that after breaking the deposit, the amount will become $148,481.58.', '10:30:00', 122, '2024-03-18 15:36:15', '2024-03-18 15:36:15'),
(372, '- Decision Making on Next Steps:\nAfter thorough discussion, the board made the decision to proceed with breaking the deposit considering the financial benefits and organizational needs.', '11:00:00', 122, '2024-03-18 15:37:08', '2024-03-18 15:37:08'),
