(376, '- Presentation on the Digital Haya Karima Trucks :\n- Mr. Amin presented details of the digital Haya Karima trucks, emphasizing their role in providing education and connectivity to underserved communities.', '10:30:00', 123, '2024-03-18 19:40:41', '2024-03-18 19:40:41'),
