(381, '- Discussion on Available Options :\n\nThe finance team presented available options for utilizing the donated funds, considering the restrictions in transferring money outside the United States.', '10:00:00', 124, '2024-03-18 20:29:19', '2024-03-18 20:30:48'),
(382, '- Decision Making on Fund Utilization or Refund Process:\n\n- A discussion ensued regarding whether to utilize the donated funds for other activities within the organization or initiate a refund process for members.\n\n-The legal team provided insights into the implications and requirements for initiating a refund process.', '10:20:00', 124, '2024-03-18 20:30:26', '2024-03-18 20:30:39'),
